## Requirements

In addition to being a Teams App , Assignments does have a set of additional requirements to be used within Assignments. See https://aka.ms/AssignmentsRequirements for full requirements for using Teams Apps in Assignments  

## Enabling Microsoft Teams application

After you have created and published your app for Assignments, Teams needs to enable the app for the Assignment App. Fill out this form https://aka.ms/AssignmentsAppRequest to get your app enabled.

